            <h2>Paris - The City of Light</h2>
            <section>
                <p>Paris, the capital of France, is one of the most popular tourist destinations in the world. Known for its art, history, and culture, the city attracts millions of visitors each year. A must-see is the Eiffel Tower, and the Louvre Museum is home to some of the world's most famous works of art.</p>
