            <section>
                <h3>Travel Tips for Paris</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Learn a few basic French phrases; locals appreciate the effort.</li>
                    <li>Visit the Eiffel Tower early in the morning to avoid crowds.</li>
                    <li>Always keep a map or a GPS app for easy navigation through the city.</li>
                </ul>
